## 4. Relationships

### One-to-One Relationships

- User → UserRole
- User → CustomerProfile

### One-to-Many Relationships

- Category → Products
- Product → ProductVariants
- Supplier → Products
- ProductVariant → ModifierGroups
- ModifierGroup → ModifierOptions
- CustomerProfile → Orders
- Order → OrderItems
- Order → Payments
- ProductVariant → OrderItems
- SalesImportBatch → DailySales
- ProductVariant → DailySales

### Many-to-Many Relationships Through Join Tables

- ProductVariant ↔ InventoryItem through VariantInventoryUsage
- ModifierOption ↔ InventoryItem through ModifierInventoryUsage
- OrderItem ↔ ModifierOption through OrderItemModifier

